		<div class="comment-content" itemprop="commentText">
			
			<p>The more I think about bitcoin, the more I realise that this might be the strongest weapon against statism there is. People who start using bitcoin will have an advantage over those who don&#8217;t. And once it establishes itself as a commonly used currency the welfare state is basically finished. And the more people are using it, the less volatile it gets. But it won&#8217;t happen over night. As the comments here show, and as my own thought process proves to me, it will take time for people to understand this new concept. Trust needs to be earned.</p>
		</div>

